const size = {
    mobileVS: '20em',
    mobileS: '22em',
    mobileM: '23em',
    mobileP: '25em',
    duo: '33em',
    landscape: '40em',
    tablet: '48em',
    laptopS: '64em',
    laptopM: '85em',
    laptopL: '90em',
    desktop: '160em'
}


export const device = {
    mobileVS: `(min-width: ${size.mobileVS})`,
    mobileS: `(min-width: ${size.mobileS})`,
    mobileM: `(min-width: ${size.mobileM})`,
    mobileP: `(min-width: ${size.mobileP})`,
    duo: `(min-width: ${size.duo})`,
    landscape: `(min-width: ${size.landscape})`,
    tablet: `(min-width: ${size.tablet})`,
    laptopS: `(min-width: ${size.laptopS})`,
    laptopM: `(min-width: ${size.laptopM})`,
    laptopL: `(min-width: ${size.laptopL})`,
    desktop: `(min-width: ${size.desktop})`
}
